WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:29.000
♪♪

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:36.000
KIRI Dad, I know you think I'm crazy.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:43.000
But I feel her.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:48.000
I hear her heart beat.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:57.000
She's so close.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:06.000
JAKE SULLY So what does her heartbeat sound like?

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.000
KIRI Mighty.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:17.000
♪♪

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:26.000
NA'VI Woo!

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:30.000
TONOWARI We cannot let you bring your war here.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:33.000
LO'AK Outcast, that's all they see.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:36.000
TSIREYA I see you.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:40.000
♪♪

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:45.000
LO'AK The Way of Water connects all things.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.000
Before your birth...

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:52.000
...and after your death.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:56.000
NEYTIRI This is our home!

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:59.000
JAKE SULLY I need you with me.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:09.000
And I need you to be strong.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:10.000
Strong heart.